elements.title: Johanna Quaas
elements.contents: ... that Johanna Quaas (pictured), the world's oldest competitive gymnast, did a tandem skydive from about 3,000 meters (9,800 ft) in 2016, dedicating it to Queen Elizabeth II?

elements.title: Stefan Keil
